</li>
<li>
<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
<cite id="CITEREFCarol_M._Swain2002" class="citation book cs1">——— (2002). <span class="id-lock-registration" title="Free registration required"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/newwhitenational0000swai"><i>The New White Nationalism in America: Its Challenge to Integration</i></a></span>. Cambridge University Press. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a> <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-521-54558-7" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-521-54558-7"><bdi>978-0-521-54558-7</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+New+White+Nationalism+in+America%3A+Its+Challenge+to+Integration&amp;rft.pub=Cambridge+University+Press&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-521-54558-7&amp;rft.au=Carol+M.+Swain&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fnewwhitenational0000swai&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACarol+M.+Swain" class="Z3988"></span>
